
  Latias    Dragon Type Pokémon

  LATIAS is highly sensitive to 
  the emotions of people.  If it 
  senses any hostility, Latias 
  ruffles the feathers all over 
  its body and cries shrilly to 
  intimidate the foe. 
  Single Stage Evolution Pokémon

